Package: dtametaTMB
Title: Diagnostic Test Accuracy Meta-Analysis using Template Model Builder
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person("Claus", "Nowak", email = "claus.nowak@donau-uni.ac.at", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Fits the hierarchical summary receiver operating characteristic (HSROC) 
    model of Rutter and Gatsonis (2001), the bivariate binomial-normal model of 
    Reitsma et al. (2005), and the threshold-based bivariate time-to-event model of
    Hoyer et al. (2018) using Template Model Builder (TMB).
